# OISST
Optimally intepolated sea surface temperature, from NOAA.

[Homepage](https://www.ncei.noaa.gov/products/optimum-interpolation-sst)  
Download location: 
* THREDDS catalog accessible from homepage.
* Alternative download location via the Physical Sciences Laboratory [here](https://psl.noaa.gov/data/gridded/data.noaa.oisst.v2.highres.html)

**Download procedure**
*From PSL*
* Easiest: `.nc` files available from PSL can be downloaded more easily
```
wget https://downloads.psl.noaa.gov/Datasets/noaa.oisst.v2.highres/sst.mon.mean.nc
```
* NOTE that it is not completely clear whether this is v2 or v2.1

*From NCEI*
* Download recursively from THREDDS catalog using `wget`
